quran[10{c,v,t}:
10,79,aur firaon ne hukum diya ke sab kaamil fungado garon ko hamaray paas le aao
10,80,jab jadugar aeye to moose ne un se kaha tum ko jo daalna hai daalo
10,81,jab unhon ne ( apni rassiyon aur lathyon ko ) dala to moose ne kaha ke jo cheezein tum ( bana kar ) laaye ho jaadoo hai khuda is ko bhi naist vnabod kardey ga. khuda shariron ke kaam sanvara nahi karta
10,82,aur khuda apne hukum se sach ko sach hi kardey ga agarchay gunehgaar bura hi manen
10,83,to moose par koi imaan nah laya. magar is ki qoum mein se chand larke ( aur woh bhi ) firaon aur is ke ahal darbaar se drtay drtay ke kahin woh un ko aafat mein nah phansa day. aur firaon mulk mein mutaqabbir o mutaghalib aur ( kibar o kufr ) mein hadd se barha howa tha
10,84,aur moose ne kaha ke bhaio! agar tum khuda par imaan laaye ho to agar ( dil se ) farmanbardar ho to isi par bharosa rakho
10,85,to woh bolay ke hum khuda hi par bharosa rakhtay hain. ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ko zalim logon ke haath se azmaish mein nah daal
10,86,aur apni rehmat se qoum kufar se nijaat bakhash
10,87,aur hum ne moose aur is ke bhai ki taraf wahi bhaije ke apne logon ke liye misar mein ghar banaao aur apne gharon ko qibla ( yani masjiden ) thehrao aur namaz parho. aur mominon ko khushkhabri suna do
10,88,aur moose ne kaha ae hamaray perwar-digaar to ne firaon aur is ke sardaro ko duniya ki zindagi mein ( bohat sa ) sazu barg aur maal vzr day rakha hai. ae perwar-digaar un ka maal yeh hai ke tairay raste se gumraah kar dein. ae perwar-digaar un ke maal ko barbaad kardey aur un ke dilon ko sakht kardey ke imaan nah layein jab taq azaab alim nah dekh len
